Download Pillar for Linux :

wget -O- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pillar-markup/book-skeleton/master/download.sh | bash


In direcotry where Pillar is installed Pillar command to export .pillar files to .html files :

./export --to=html file.pillar > file.html


Documentation for Pillar syntax :

See 5 minutes tutorial : https://ci.inria.fr/pharo-contribution/job/EnterprisePharoBook/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/PillarChap/Pillar.pillar.html